item.title: About
item.description: Music dataset Purpose Music Dataset is a platform that collects people’s emotional responses after listening to classical music. By labeling music with certain tags, I hope the dataset can solve the complexity involved in the abstract components of music, thus allowing it to be analyzed and classified by computer. The ultimate aim is to improve the field of music machine learning by providing a dataset for training. How to use it?

item.description: Music Datatset is a platform that collects people’s emotional responses after listening to classical music. By labeling music with certain tags, I hope the dataset can solve the complexity involved in the abstract components of music, thus allowing it to be analyzed and classified by computer. The ultimate aim is to improve the field of music machine learning by providing dataset for training. To read more
